{"tid":622275,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[痴撚線] 屍體防腐液誤輸入體內 俄女病人「極度痛苦」下死去","createTime":"2018-04-09T04:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T05:03:37.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e93690790704953c0beaba8140d389465413cf","tid":622275,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:43:54.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一名女子接受手術時，醫生誤將屍體防腐劑誤當鹽水輸入她體內，導致她在極度痛苦下死亡。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的費佳耶娃（Ekaterina Fedyaeva 圖）到西部烏里揚諾夫斯克（Ulyanovsk）一間醫院接受例行手術，其間要吊鹽水，但醫生卻誤將含甲醛的浸屍防腐液福爾馬林（Formalin）輸入其靜脈。<br />\n費佳耶娃的媽媽加林娜（Galina Baryshnikova）指，費佳耶娃在麻醉蘇醒後肚痛嘔吐，身體抽搐，渾身不停顫抖，兩天後陷入昏迷，要儀器維生，心臟多次停頓。加林娜說，當時她與女婿伊戈爾（Igor）都不知道費佳耶娃被輸入福爾馬林，身體正「從內被侵蝕」。<br />\n費佳耶娃之後被送往莫斯科一間醫院，證實被輸入福爾馬林。醫生開了52種藥救她，她的確曾一度蘇醒，但最終因為多重器官衰竭死亡。<br />\n加林娜指烏里揚諾夫斯克醫院的主刀醫生知道犯錯，卻沒有即時採取補救行動，只叫她不要擔心，主任醫生之後才承認出錯，但費佳耶娃心肺肝都已衰竭。加林娜指醫護人員「謀殺」了她的女兒。"},{"pid":"0819514e1ef57617e17c5f1d3e6c30318854f91a","tid":622275,"uid":54728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:44:44.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2453fbac7a6e2bc9b78d8fd74efd9e236eb0d42","tid":622275,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkg